data.description: Spacious/inviting, 4 BR 2.5 bath home on a quiet street located in Portsmouth. Traditional layout on main level with living room and dining room, 1/2 bath, kitchen w/SS appliances, granite counters, laundry and LVP and tile flooring.  Large, 1st floor primary bedroom with full bath completes the space.  The 2nd floor offers 3 large bedrooms, a full bathroom, and a large loft/bonus room for entertaining.  The home has a fully-fenced yard with deck and storage shed, too.  Roof (30-yr arch), HVAC, hot water heater were replaced in the last several months.  All other improvements were done in the last 10 years.  Close to bases, shipyard, shopping, hospitals, and easy access to interstates.  **VA Assumption @ 2.5% rate - inquire about details.**  Make this your Happy Place!
